{"tid":2394050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國都無零確診：中國增30人確診　上海有3宗新增本土病例","createTime":"2021-02-04T02:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T02:23:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee1f1cc2084768b5bb4b75df824f93d804b38932","tid":2394050,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:17:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574004-20210204.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574004-20210204.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=16f426ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574004-20210204.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cd1417a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574004-20210204.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中國過去一日，新增30人確診感染新型冠狀病毒，當中17宗是本土病例；死亡個案並無增加。<br />\n<br />\n其中3宗新增本土病例來自上海，兩人住在黃浦區，一人住在寶山區。<br />\n<br />\n市衛健委說，市及區相關部門已組成聯合專家隊伍，全面展開流行病學調查，追蹤排查相關人員，已對3名新增患者的相關接觸人員，進行集中隔離醫學觀察，並徹底消毒3人活動過的場所。"},{"pid":"8b07352b6197f23e003570b4e26a51d2236951bd","tid":2394050,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:18:50.000Z","msg":"港共:開關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05c1e0a271d6b187d1481d463e0b21e0340eee9","tid":2394050,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多過香港點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5d7160d847cd119b672797708d5c02f53939fa","tid":2394050,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c05c1e0a271d6b187d1481d463e0b21e0340eee9","tid":2394050,"uid":173271,"lik